===Noun===
'''drēam''' {{m}} (pl. ''drēamas'')

# [[joy]], [[pleasure]], [[ecstasy]]
#: ''Ðær biþ drincendra dream se micla'': there is the great joy of drinkers.
# [[music]], [[song]]
#: ''Iohannes gehyrde swylce bymena dream'': John heard, as it were, the sound of trumpets.

